<h1>Booking Confirmed!</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.full_name %> and <%= @friend.user.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Your booking has been confirmed with the following details:</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 5px;">
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @booking.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @booking.start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> - <%= @booking.end_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></p>
  <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= @booking.duration %> hours</p>
  <p><strong>Service Category:</strong> <%= @booking.service_category.name %></p>
  <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> <%= @booking.total_amount.format %></p>
</div>

<% if @booking.notes.present? %>
  <p><strong>Additional Notes:</strong></p>
  <p><%= @booking.notes %></p>
<% end %>

<p>You will receive a reminder 24 hours before the booking.</p>

<p>If you need to cancel or modify this booking, please do so at least 24 hours in advance through the website.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  The Rent A Friend Team
</p>
